No. 680,

Misc.

Kimbrough v. United States. Petitioner pro se. Solicitor General Rankin, Assistant Attorney General Wilkey and Beatrice Rosenberg for the United States.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit granted. Case transferred to the appellate docket.
